                    <span>I haven't read all of the recepies. However, at the moment I am very happy with this book.
<br />
<br />The chapter on input validation is really well done. It is easy to start with what the book offers and extend it to something else.
<br />
<br />The chapters on error handling and tracing are also very good. 
<br />
<br />This book has clear examples and good code. I am happy with it.</span>
                  
              
